      <h3><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-plane"></i> Airlift Deliveries</h3>
      <ul class="list-unstyled">
        <li>Hundred of available dropzones</li>
        <li>Available overseas</li>
        <li>Supplier discounts</li>
      </ul>
      <p> <%= button_to "Purchase", root_path, class: "btn btn-supply" %></p>
    </div>
  </div> <!-- row text-center -->

  <div class="container get-help-today">
    <div class="row">

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <h2>Get Help Today!</h2>
        <ul class="nav nav-tabs">
          <li> <%= link_to "Deliveries", root_path, class: "active" %></li>
          <li> <%= link_to "Deals", root_path %></li>
          <li> <%= link_to "Browse current relief programs", root_path %></li>
        </ul>

        <div class="tab-content">
          <div class="tab-pane fade active", id="time">
            <p>Deliveries</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tab-pane fade", id="deals">
            <p>Deals here</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tab-pane fade", id="forecast">
            <p>Programs</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='col-md-3 col-md-offset-1'>
        <div class='panel-group'>

          <div class='panel panel-success'>
            <div class='panel-heading'>
              <h4 class='panel-title'>
                <a href='#currentPackages' data-toggle="collapse" data-parent=".panel-group">Offered Packages</a>
              </h4>
            </div>
            <div id='currentPackages' class='collapse panel-collapse in'>
              <div class='panel-body'>
                <p>Current Packages</p>
                <ul class='list-unstyled'>
                  <li><i class='glyphicon glyphicon-leaf'></i> Food Package</li>
                  <li><i class='glyphicon glyphicon-tint'></i> Water Package</li>
                  <li><i class='glyphicon glyphicon-plane'></i> Airlift Package</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='panel panel-warning'>
            <div class='panel-heading'>
              <h4 class='panel-title'>
                <a href='#weatherAlert' data-toggle="collapse" data-parent=".panel-group">Weather Alert</a>
              </h4>
            </div>
            <div id='weatherAlert' class='collapse panel-collapse'>
              <div class='panel-body'>
                <p>The National Weather Service has issued a CAT 4 hurricane in the Southeast. Our suppliers are looking forward to helping</p>
                <ul class='list-unstyled'>
                  <li><strong>February 9th, 21:43</strong></li>
                  <li><strong>May 18, 19:82</strong></li>
                  <li><strong>July 4, 08:42</strong></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='panel panel-danger'>
            <div class='panel-heading'>
              <h4 class='panel-title'>
                <a href='#airliftSafety' data-toggle="collapse" data-parent=".panel-group">Transportation Generals Warning: Airlift Safety</a>
              </h4>
            </div>
            <div id='airliftSafety' class='collapse panel-collapse'>
              <div class='panel-body'>
                <p>Our Airlift pilots are highly trained and qualified to make calls on the base landing zones in a location of extreme disaster. Please keep in contact with them if you plan for a delivery system after a disaster has already begun.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

    </div> <!-- row -->
  </div> <!-- container get-help-today -->
</div> <!-- container -->
